content:
Assign Permissions to Admins and Users

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Users, and then select Users. 
Click the name of the user to whom you want to assign permissions. 
Click Permission Set Assignments | Edit Assignments. 
Assign the user admin or user permissions: 
To assign admin permissions, select the Revenue Intelligence Media Analytics Admin permission set. 
To assign the user user permissions, select the Revenue Intelligence Media Analytics User permission set. 
Add the permission set, and then save your changes.
